{"tid":2356963,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"胡志偉涉違反保釋條件無交旅行證件　今午西九法院提堂","createTime":"2021-01-07T06:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T07:26:45.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"885bee6f7b00eba51b1c3d9751d74c2f0c33cd49","tid":2356963,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T06:17:36.000Z","msg":"民主黨前主席胡志偉昨日（6日）被警方拘捕，被指涉嫌違反《港區國安法》，其後被帶到黃大仙警署。據了解，他早前被控涉煽惑他人參與七一前後遊行等，法庭要求交出旅行證件，但他沒有提交，故涉嫌違反保釋條件。據悉，胡志偉今日（7日）將被帶到西九龍裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20210107/s00001/1609999819250/%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af-%e8%83%a1%e5%bf%97%e5%81%89%e6%b6%89%e9%81%95%e5%8f%8d%e4%bf%9d%e9%87%8b%e6%a2%9d%e4%bb%b6%e7%84%a1%e4%ba%a4%e6%97%85%e8%a1%8c%e8%ad%89%e4%bb%b6-%e4%bb%8a%e5%8d%88%e8%a5%bf%e4%b9%9d%e6%b3%95%e9%99%a2%e6%8f%90%e5%a0%82?web_push=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20210107%2Fs00001%2F1609999819250%2F%25e6%25b6%2588%25e6%2581%25af-%25e8%2583%25a1%25e5%25bf%2597%25e5%2581%2589%25e6%25b6%2589%25e9%2581%2595%25e5%258f%258d%25e4%25bf%259d%25e9%2587%258b%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25bb%25b6%25e7%2584%25a1%25e4%25ba%25a4%25e6%2597%2585%25e8%25a1%258c%25e8%25ad%2589%25e4%25bb%25b6-%25e4%25bb%258a%25e5%258d%2588%25e8%25a5%25bf%25e4%25b9%259d%25e6%25b3%2595%25e9%2599%25a2%25e6%258f%2590%25e5%25a0%2582%3Fweb_push%3D1&d=tgCcTb3Ji4LFIEkqsM1g5uQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=a7dc82ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20210107%2Fs00001%2F1609999819250%2F%25e6%25b6%2588%25e6%2581%25af-%25e8%2583%25a1%25e5%25bf%2597%25e5%2581%2589%25e6%25b6%2589%25e9%2581%2595%25e5%258f%258d%25e4%25bf%259d%25e9%2587%258b%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25bb%25b6%25e7%2584%25a1%25e4%25ba%25a4%25e6%2597%2585%25e8%25a1%258c%25e8%25ad%2589%25e4%25bb%25b6-%25e4%25bb%258a%25e5%258d%2588%25e8%25a5%25bf%25e4%25b9%259d%25e6%25b3%25